<div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The extension value string.\n","docLink":"./Std/Http/Data/Chunk.html#Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionValue.value","kind":"def","line":113,"name":"Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionValue.value","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Std/Http/Data/Chunk.lean#L113-L113"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Data/Chunk.html#Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionValue.mk\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">Chunk</span>.<span class=\"name\">ExtensionValue</span>.<span class=\"name\">mk</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">value</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>) →\n  <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Tactics.html#autoParam\">autoParam</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Std/Http/Data/Chunk.html#Std.Http.Chunk.IsValidExtensionValue\">Std.Http.Chunk.IsValidExtensionValue</a> <span class=\"fn\">value</span>)</span>\n      <a href=\"./Std/Http/Data/Chunk.html#Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionValue.isValidExtensionValue\">Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionValue.isValidExtensionValue._autoParam</a></span> →\n    <a href=\"./Std/Http/Data/Chunk.html#Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionValue\">Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionValue</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Std/Http/Data/Chunk.html#Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionValue.mk","kind":"ctor","line":98,"name":"Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionValue.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Std/Http/Data/Chunk.lean#L98-L119"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">structure</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Data/Chunk.html#Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionValue\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">Chunk</span>.<span class=\"name\">ExtensionValue</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A validated chunk extension value that ensures all characters conform to HTTP standards per RFC 9112 §7.1.1.\nExtension values appear in chunked transfer encoding as metadata associated with extension names.\n\nNote: UTF-8 encoding is not supported. The quoting mechanism is strict and only permits escaping\nspecific values. Additionally, the library does not support obs-text, which means certain UTF-8\ncharacters or values outside of token, qdtext, and the limited set of escapable characters cannot be\nencoded.\n\nReference: https://httpwg.org/specs/rfc9112.html#chunked.extension\n","docLink":"./Std/Http/Data/Chunk.html#Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionValue","kind":"structure","line":98,"name":"Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionValue","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Std/Http/Data/Chunk.lean#L98-L119"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Data/Chunk.html#Std.Http.Chunk.IsValidExtensionValue\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">Chunk</span>.<span class=\"name\">IsValidExtensionValue</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A proposition asserting that `s` is a valid extension value, meaning every character passes\n`Char.quotedStringChar` (i.e. is `qdtext` or a valid `quoted-pair` payload).\n\nReference: https://httpwg.org/specs/rfc9112.html#chunked.extension\n","docLink":"./Std/Http/Data/Chunk.html#Std.Http.Chunk.IsValidExtensionValue","kind":"def","line":89,"name":"Std.Http.Chunk.IsValidExtensionValue","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Std/Http/Data/Chunk.lean#L89-L96"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Data/Chunk.html#Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionName.ofString!\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">Chunk</span>.<span class=\"name\">ExtensionName</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofString!</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Std/Http/Data/Chunk.html#Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionName\">ExtensionName</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Creates an `ExtensionName` from a string, panicking with an error message if the string contains\ninvalid characters or is empty.\n","docLink":"./Std/Http/Data/Chunk.html#Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionName.ofString!","kind":"def","line":78,"name":"Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionName.ofString!","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Std/Http/Data/Chunk.lean#L78-L85"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Data/Chunk.html#Std.Http.Chunk.ExtensionName.ofString?\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">Chunk</span>.<span class=\"name\">ExtensionName</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofString?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">